00:00:20.413 --> 00:00:22.364
hot men eynike vagonen

00:00:23.873 --> 00:00:27.343
ibergelozn. ir gedenkt nit vos far a larger dos iz gevezn?

00:00:25.746 --> 00:00:26.662
ye.

