do- yetst hob ikh dermont. s'iz geven, er hot geheysn Treblinke.

00:00:31.534 --> 00:00:34.312
un zey, fun dem lager Treblinke

00:00:34.470 --> 00:00:39.090
hot keyner nit gekent aroyskumen. m- m'hot, m'hot zey ale mentshn farbrent.

00:00:39.381 --> 00:00:41.232
undz hot men gefirt,

00:00:41.232 --> 00:00:42.919
mir hobn nit gevust avu,

00:00:43.684 --> 00:00:46.761
un m'hot undz azoy gefirt biz AUSCHWITZ.

00:00:46.761 --> 00:00:48.369
dem zibetn

00:00:48.426 --> 00:00:49.671
FEBRAL

00:00:49.671 --> 00:00:51.238
hob ikh ongekumen

00:00:52.138 --> 00:00:54.005
AU- tsu AUSCHWITZ.

00:00:54.147 --> 00:00:57.178
un m- un m'hot aroysgetribn undz fun di vagones:

00:00:57.488 --> 00:00:59.534
"SCHNELL! SCHNELL! SCHNELL MACHEN!" un,

00:00:59.534 --> 00:01:02.511
un m'hot undz geharget mit nagaykes, mit altsding,

00:01:02.736 --> 00:01:05.987
un s'iz geshtanen zeyer a hoykher ofitsir,

00:01:06.027 --> 00:01:08.082
zeyer a sheyner man,

00:01:08.082 --> 00:01:10.836
mit altsding, mit, mit aza shtekele:

00:01:10.836 --> 00:01:12.003
"RECHTS.

00:01:12.003 --> 00:01:12.733
LINKS.

00:01:12.733 --> 00:01:13.727
RECHTS.

00:01:13.727 --> 00:01:14.255
LINKS."

00:01:14.886 --> 00:01:16.500
mir hot er geshikt

00:01:17.417 --> 00:01:18.491
rekhts,

00:01:19.493 --> 00:01:23.064
un mayn froy mitn kind, er iz geven oyf l- oyf links.

00:01:24.150 --> 00:01:30.180
kh'hob gekrign a- mitn shte- mit a shtekn do ibern kop. dos ⟨UNK⟩b ikh her nit azoy gut.

00:01:30.180 --> 00:01:33.116
un ⟨a⟩ nokh a mol ⟨mir⟩ a shtekn. ikh hob zikh oyfgehoybn,

00:01:33.116 --> 00:01:35.062
hob ikh gezen vi mayn froy

00:01:35.068 --> 00:01:39.191
⟨shteyt shoyn⟩ in, oy- oyf a mashin, a ofene mashin,

00:01:39.191 --> 00:01:43.418
mitn kind, un zi makht tsu mir z- z- zol, zol dermonen,

00:01:43.418 --> 00:01:46.430
vos mir hobn getantst oyf a khasene dem vals,

00:01:46.430 --> 00:01:48.966
UNIVERSITY vals hobn mir getantst.

00:01:48.966 --> 00:01:50.857
un m- ⟨UNK⟩ert mir veln derzen,

00:01:51.437 --> 00:01:53.219
do- dortn ⟨m'vet⟩ derzen.

00:01:53.462 --> 00:01:54.114
⟨ze-⟩

00:01:56.162 --> 00:02:00.473
un, un dernokh hot men undz ale ⟨ar⟩oysgeshtelt, di vos iz geven oyf rekhts.

00:02:00.617 --> 00:02:02.535
me fregt, vos in baruf.

00:02:02.676 --> 00:02:04.627
hob ikh gezogt, "ikh bin a shnayder."

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:07.681
ikh bin azoy a shnayder azoy vi ir zent a shnayder.

00:02:09.003 --> 00:02:11.083
s- m'hot undz avekgefirt nokh

00:02:11.083 --> 00:02:13.478
BIRKENAU. nit, nit nokh AUSCHWITZ,

00:02:13.478 --> 00:02:17.351
nor BIRKENAU iz geven. dos iz dray kilometer fun AUSCHWITZ.

00:02:17.661 --> 00:02:21.772
dortn undz avekgefirt, hobn mir geven zeks vokhn tsayt.

00:02:21.897 --> 00:02:23.747
m'hot tsetrogn tsigl,

00:02:24.090 --> 00:02:27.189
 andere shvere arbet, mit altsding.

00:02:27.330 --> 00:02:29.788
ober undzer blok-eltster

00:02:30.013 --> 00:02:33.208
iz gevezn a yid. oyb s'iz aykh bakant

00:02:33.208 --> 00:02:35.745
Yitskhok Grinboym's zun.

00:02:36.004 --> 00:02:40.284
Yitskhok Grinboym iz geven in Poyln a deputat in seym,

00:02:41.016 --> 00:02:45.397
un der zun iz geven a firer fun der Komunistisher Partey in Poyln.

00:02:46.922 --> 00:02:49.379
dernokh hot er antlofn nokh Pariz.

00:02:49.909 --> 00:02:52.621
fun Pariz hobn daytshn mistame im gekhapt,

00:02:52.621 --> 00:02:55.850
un m'hot im gebrakht in, in, in BIRKENAU,

00:02:55.866 --> 00:02:58.408
un er iz gevorn a blok-eltster,

00:02:58.549 --> 00:03:01.175
der, der firer fun, fun, fu- fun barak.

00:03:01.637 --> 00:03:03.875
un er hot undz gezogt azoy:

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:06.688
"⟨SŁUCHAJCIE, ŻYDŻI⟩.

00:03:06.688 --> 00:03:09.680
UNK ⟨NIE⟩ UNK ⟨BĘDZIECIE SPOKOJNI⟩,

00:03:10.041 --> 00:03:12.077
⟨TO JUTRO BĘDZIECIE TUTA⟩."

00:03:12.370 --> 00:03:14.645
un mir hobn nit ⟨gevust vos⟩ heyst "⟨TUTA⟩."

00:03:14.645 --> 00:03:15.910
az- er zogt azoy:

00:03:15.910 --> 00:03:17.443
"hert zikh ayn, yidn.

00:03:17.702 --> 00:03:20.297
oyb ir vet nit zayn shtil un ruik,

00:03:20.297 --> 00:03:24.125
vet ⟨zey⟩ geyn morgn." un morgn, dos iz geven di KREMATORIUM.

00:03:24.925 --> 00:03:25.866
er hot es,

00:03:25.866 --> 00:03:28.732
 AUSCHWITZ ligt in di Karpatn.

00:03:29.076 --> 00:03:33.128
zeyer vintik un kalt, geferlekh, erter.

00:03:33.128 --> 00:03:37.305
m'hot undz gedarft aroystraybn tsum apel zeks a zeyger in der fri.

00:03:37.311 --> 00:03:40.646
er hot undz aroysgetribn finf a zeyger in der fri.

00:03:40.669 --> 00:03:44.580
un er hot ⟨zey⟩ nit gelozt zikh nit raybn a mentsh in a mentsh, azoy o,

00:03:44.580 --> 00:03:45.371
nit.

00:03:46.103 --> 00:03:50.721
un er hot undz zeyer shlekht, shlekht bahandlt. un mir hobn ⟨zikh⟩ bavundert,

00:03:50.828 --> 00:03:53.297
a zun fun aza tatn,

00:03:53.297 --> 00:03:55.279
fun aza bavustn tatn,

00:03:55.279 --> 00:03:57.689
un a- un er aleyn a Komunist,

00:03:57.898 --> 00:04:00.575
zol zayn aza merder ⟨aza in der velt⟩.

00:04:01.037 --> 00:04:03.005
epes got hot geholfn,

00:04:03.062 --> 00:04:05.216
nokh a por vokhn tsayt,

00:04:05.678 --> 00:04:08.017
m'hot im tsugenumen in a ander ort,

00:04:09.272 --> 00:04:11.206
un s'iz gekumen a polyak,

00:04:11.415 --> 00:04:12.855
a blok-eltster.

00:04:13.069 --> 00:04:17.091
in der tsayt ven der blo- der polyak geve- gevorn blok-eltster,

00:04:17.091 --> 00:04:19.256
iz ongekumen di tsigayners

00:04:19.414 --> 00:04:21.720
fun Rumenye, fun Ungarn.

00:04:21.726 --> 00:04:25.078
zeyer raykhe, zeyer sheyn ongeton, mit altsding.

00:04:26.805 --> 00:04:27.963
un,

00:04:28.594 --> 00:04:31.338
un zey hobn nit gevolt nit esn di esn zeyere.

00:04:32.374 --> 00:04:36.215
hot genumen der polyak zeyere esn un undz gegebn.

00:04:37.318 --> 00:04:39.320
di esn vos m'hot gegebn...?

00:04:39.012 --> 00:04:40.989
di, di, vo- vos di, di tsigayners,

00:04:40.989 --> 00:04:42.651
m'hot gedarft gebn t- far di tsigayners,

00:04:42.651 --> 00:04:45.999
hobn di tsigayners nit gevolt esn. zey hobn gehat eygene esn nokh.

00:04:46.026 --> 00:04:49.139
dos iz e- dernokh, hobn zey gelekt di finger nebekh UNK.

00:04:49.139 --> 00:04:50.132
zey hot men ale

00:04:50.132 --> 00:04:53.529
avekgefirt in di KREMATORIUM nokh far, nokh frier nokh vi di yidn.

00:04:53.755 --> 00:04:54.711
dos o.

00:04:56.337 --> 00:04:58.997
un der polyak ⟨geven⟩, gezogt azoy tsu undz:

00:04:59.138 --> 00:05:00.988
"hert zikh ayn, ⟨ŻYDKI⟩.

00:05:01.197 --> 00:05:03.638
s'vet nokh shaynen far undz di zun

00:05:04.588 --> 00:05:06.995
oy- oykhet, abi ir zayt ruik."

00:05:07.407 --> 00:05:10.212
nor ikh, ikh vil aykh epes zogn f-

00:05:10.225 --> 00:05:12.609
kh'ho- kh- vos ikh hob aykh nit gezogt frier.

00:05:12.609 --> 00:05:15.044
ven m'hot undz gebrakht nokh BIRKENAU,

00:05:15.118 --> 00:05:17.289
hot men undz arayngetribn in a barak,

00:05:17.464 --> 00:05:19.837
un m'hot undz geheysn oystun naket,

00:05:20.299 --> 00:05:24.056
un m'hot gezogt, "gits ayere gold, ayere zilber,

00:05:24.079 --> 00:05:26.418
un oyb nit, vet men aykh shisn."

00:05:27.623 --> 00:05:29.625
un dernokh, naketerheyt,

00:05:29.884 --> 00:05:32.189
dos iz geven in FEBRAL MONTH,

00:05:32.189 --> 00:05:34.032
un m'hot ⟨zey⟩ getribn in a,

00:05:34.032 --> 00:05:34.968
in BATH,

00:05:34.968 --> 00:05:35.677
i-

00:05:35.677 --> 00:05:37.455
a kaltn SHOWER.

00:05:38.167 --> 00:05:39.903
un oyb ir hot zikh oysgedreyt

00:05:39.903 --> 00:05:42.561
fun SHOWER a bisele UNK se geyt nit der WATER,

00:05:42.563 --> 00:05:44.554
hobn geshtanen di polyakn,

00:05:44.554 --> 00:05:48.947
di, di ⟨shtub-eltster⟩ heyst es, un mit a shtekn, un m'hot undz geharget.

00:05:49.476 --> 00:05:50.502
tsurik

00:05:50.502 --> 00:05:54.296
loyfndik tsu dem barak ze- no- nokh, nokhn, nokhn BATH,

00:05:54.589 --> 00:05:57.688
hobn mentshn glaykh geshtorbn, PNEUMONIA,

00:05:58.521 --> 00:06:01.299
un m'hot a sakh mentshn ni- nit gekent

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:02.953
be- do- do- dos

00:06:03.415 --> 00:06:04.691
ibertrogn.

00:06:04.765 --> 00:06:05.664
dos o.

00:06:05.664 --> 00:06:06.694
un ikh,

00:06:06.694 --> 00:06:09.816
ikh, ⟨ikh⟩ hob gehat efsher a bisl mazl un ikh hob geblibn lebn

00:06:09.816 --> 00:06:13.208
un dernokh hob ikh alts geven in, in BIRKENAU

00:06:13.208 --> 00:06:15.221
nor zeks vokhn tsayt,

00:06:15.345 --> 00:06:17.819
hot men undz gebrakht nokh AUSCHWITZ.

00:06:18.518 --> 00:06:21.465
nokh AUSCHWITZ hot men ⟨undz⟩ geshtelt fragn,

00:06:22.585 --> 00:06:26.781
"vos b- vo- dayn fakh, ⟨dayn baruf⟩." hob ikh gezogt, "ikh bin a shnayder."

00:06:27.192 --> 00:06:30.358
ikh aro- arayn ⟨in di⟩ UNK ⟨tsu di⟩ shnayderay.

00:06:30.651 --> 00:06:34.948
zogt der daytsh, "ver es vet nit zayn keyn shnayder, zogt a lign,

00:06:35.106 --> 00:06:37.281
vet men im glaykh shisn oyfn ort."

00:06:38.160 --> 00:06:40.162
hob ikh zikh umgekert tsurik

00:06:41.215 --> 00:06:43.740
un ikh hob gearbet oyfn hoyf.

00:06:43.881 --> 00:06:45.400
proste arbet.

00:06:46.193 --> 00:06:48.991
 tsigl, brukirn,

00:06:48.991 --> 00:06:51.269
leygn shteyner, leygn breter,

00:06:51.269 --> 00:06:53.004
grobn griber,

00:06:53.500 --> 00:06:55.198
⟨i-⟩ dos iz geven der toyt.

00:06:55.339 --> 00:06:58.775
geferlekh. un ikh hob dos altsding oysgehaltn.

00:06:59.187 --> 00:06:59.873
⟨ze-⟩

00:06:59.895 --> 00:07:01.070
azoy,

00:07:01.161 --> 00:07:02.404
un dernokh

00:07:02.528 --> 00:07:05.216
hot mir tsu- hot mir tsugenumen

00:07:05.216 --> 00:07:08.631
in a ⟨MAUERKOMMANDO⟩, dos iz a, a m- a mulyers.

00:07:08.957 --> 00:07:12.480
un ikh hob derlangt di polyakn, di m- di ⟨MULARZE⟩s

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:15.636
di tsigl un ikh hob gemakht di v- di vapne.

00:07:15.636 --> 00:07:16.640
i-

00:07:16.640 --> 00:07:20.480
ir veyst UNK vos me tut oyf, oyf di, oyf di BRICKLAYING iz dos o.

00:07:20.770 --> 00:07:24.211
un ikh hob dos altsding oysgehaltn, biz vanen s-

00:07:25.815 --> 00:07:26.619
ye.

00:07:27.925 --> 00:07:30.214
un dernokh iz gevezn apel.

00:07:31.570 --> 00:07:34.230
apel, vos me tseylt di arestantn.

00:07:35.991 --> 00:07:37.506
ot iz geven

00:07:37.506 --> 00:07:39.911
der zelber vos iz geshtanen frier,

00:07:39.911 --> 00:07:42.856
der sheyner man mitn shtekele, rekhts un links,

00:07:42.856 --> 00:07:45.806
un dos iz gevezn dokter Mengele.

00:07:47.230 --> 00:07:49.697
er hot UNK aroysgezen shlekht,

00:07:49.697 --> 00:07:51.452
hot er gegebn a ruf aroys d-

00:07:51.452 --> 00:07:53.029
dos hot geheysn a selektsye.

00:07:53.322 --> 00:07:57.495
mi yikhye un mi yomes, ver tsum lebn, ver tsum shtarbn.

00:07:58.654 --> 00:08:03.575
un UNK kukt dikh on afile me, me UNK sheyn er zet, mit a shtekn,

00:08:03.615 --> 00:08:07.282
un ikh hob gemakht dem dray mol, azoy o.

00:08:07.282 --> 00:08:10.089
i- i- i- i- i- i- i- i- ibungen

00:08:10.804 --> 00:08:12.277
un ikh hob im gezogt,

00:08:12.277 --> 00:08:17.329
"HERR OBERSCHARFÜHRER, ⟨ICH ken VIEL SCHAFFEN. ICH BIN VOLLKOM GESUND⟩."

00:08:17.385 --> 00:08:20.163
