00:08:20.355 --> 00:08:22.273
geyn tsurik in di reyen.

00:08:23.157 --> 00:08:24.326
fun shrek,

00:08:24.326 --> 00:08:27.200
als, ⟨az ikh bin shoyn⟩ geven a alter PRISONER,

00:08:27.358 --> 00:08:29.427
hot mir aroysgevorfn sh-

00:08:30.092 --> 00:08:33.765
dray geshvirn do, dray do un dray do.

00:08:33.990 --> 00:08:36.110
ikh hob nokh alts UNK dos o.

00:08:37.381 --> 00:08:39.535
un ikh hob avek in HOSPITAL.

00:08:39.745 --> 00:08:43.856
hot mir a poylisher dokter dos geefnt mit a meserl,

00:08:44.166 --> 00:08:46.674
on narkotik, on alemen,

00:08:46.714 --> 00:08:49.070
un ikh hob gehaltn azoy di hent,

00:08:49.532 --> 00:08:51.005
 un azoy d-

00:08:51.005 --> 00:08:53.812
⟨gemakht⟩ di tseyn. un er hot mir dos

00:08:54.831 --> 00:08:55.753
geshnitn.

00:08:57.531 --> 00:08:58.925
azoy geyendik,

00:08:59.067 --> 00:09:04.478
ikh hob gehat, ot, ot di ⟨MAUER⟩komande hot aroysgegangen oysern lager arbetn,

00:09:04.500 --> 00:09:06.181
mit tsivile mentshn.

00:09:06.357 --> 00:09:09.636
ikh hob zey aroysgetrogn oykhet, a hantekh un shikh.

00:09:09.636 --> 00:09:13.116
zey hobn undz gegebn broyt. a tsibele geven a shtik gold.

00:09:13.116 --> 00:09:14.231
⟨azoy⟩, dos o.

00:09:14.677 --> 00:09:17.873
