00:09:17.887 --> 00:09:19.175
hot men mir gegebn.

00:09:21.493 --> 00:09:24.660
hobn, azoy vi geyendik in reyen fun der arbet,

00:09:24.660 --> 00:09:27.916
geyt men ⟨zikh⟩ tsu, tsu zeks, tsu zibn, gegangen in a leng,

00:09:27.990 --> 00:09:31.920
un se shteyt der S.S. un me kukt ver yederer geyt.

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:34.121
di hitlen hot men gemuzt aropnemen

00:09:34.121 --> 00:09:36.472
un der orkester hot geshpilt.

00:09:37.103 --> 00:09:41.231
dos o. m'hot gemuzt geyn azoy vi di soldatn, fus tsu fus UNK.

00:09:41.389 --> 00:09:44.945
zey hobn gezen mistame bay mir az ikh hob a liter shnaps.

00:09:45.068 --> 00:09:47.154
m'hot mir gegebn a nem aroys

00:09:47.768 --> 00:09:49.196
un m'hot mir batapt

00:09:49.708 --> 00:09:53.667
un aroysgenumen dem liter shnaps mit a, mit a broyt hob ikh gehat.

00:09:55.058 --> 00:09:57.144
hob ikh gekrign far derfar

00:09:57.218 --> 00:10:00.469
dray vokhn bunker, dos heyst turme,

00:10:00.508 --> 00:10:04.071
un finf un tsvantsik hob ikh gekrign shmits,

00:10:04.103 --> 00:10:08.079
mir antshuldikn, oy- oyf di, vu di veykhe fleysh iz..

00:10:08.963 --> 00:10:11.193
di ershte shmits hob ikh gesh-

00:10:11.193 --> 00:10:12.314
geshrign,

00:10:12.490 --> 00:10:13.767
⟨gevaldevet⟩.

00:10:13.767 --> 00:10:15.774
dernokh hob ikh shoyn gornit geshpirt.

00:10:17.839 --> 00:10:20.836
der blok-eltster, der firer fun der turme,

00:10:20.961 --> 00:10:22.237
iz geven

00:10:22.716 --> 00:10:25.579
lebn Byalistok, geven zeyer a shtarker.

00:10:25.669 --> 00:10:28.018
er hot gehakt tshvekes mitn hant.

00:10:28.018 --> 00:10:30.121
er iz geve- er iz geven bavust in Poyln.

00:10:30.121 --> 00:10:31.806
er hot geheysn ⟨Kozholtshik⟩,

00:10:31.995 --> 00:10:33.290
hot er geheysn.

00:10:33.290 --> 00:10:36.345
hobn di Byalistoker tsugegangen tsu im, un m'hot gezogt,

00:10:36.418 --> 00:10:39.415
"du muzst zey rateven, dem, dem, dem,"

00:10:39.574 --> 00:10:40.732
⟨arayngefaln⟩.

00:10:40.732 --> 00:10:44.141
hot er mir gegebn esn un tsugeleygt do o,

00:10:44.451 --> 00:10:47.398
tsu di veykhe fleysh, kalte kompresn.

00:10:47.792 --> 00:10:49.409
zol di b- di blut

00:10:49.409 --> 00:10:51.144
zol avek, un mit altsding.

00:10:51.994 --> 00:10:55.143
un dernokh hot men mir gegebn ⟨STRAF⟩komande.

00:10:55.420 --> 00:10:57.096
⟨STRAF⟩komande iz

00:10:57.096 --> 00:10:58.789
eyne fun di ergste zakhn.

00:10:58.947 --> 00:11:01.607
⟨tsu m-⟩ m'hot undz gegebn grobn a grub,

