dos o.

00:11:58.515 --> 00:12:01.833
un azoy bin, hob ikh geven in, in AUSCHWITZ

00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:04.128
biz dem zibetsetn

00:12:04.489 --> 00:12:06.153
JANUAR, dakht zikh mir.

00:12:07.358 --> 00:12:10.237
gekumen di, di, dem zibetsetn JANUARY,

00:12:10.412 --> 00:12:12.974
hobn mir gezen, di shpil iz tsu ende.

00:12:12.974 --> 00:12:15.902
⟨zey⟩, di daytshn farbrenen ale papirn,

00:12:15.902 --> 00:12:17.201
