un me heyst ⟨undz⟩

00:12:19.221 --> 00:12:21.202
shteyn blaybn bay der, ba-

00:12:21.202 --> 00:12:23.884
bay di kuk- bay der kikh, ⟨iz⟩ dortn iz gevezn,

00:12:23.884 --> 00:12:25.292
aza groyser PLACE.

00:12:25.292 --> 00:12:27.449
un ⟨m'iz⟩ geblibn shteyn, m'hot oyfgeklibn,

00:12:27.473 --> 00:12:28.952
un m'hot undz gefirt.

00:12:30.021 --> 00:12:34.132
lo- ⟨loyfstrit⟩, un ver s'hot nit gekent loyfn, er iz gefaln,

00:12:34.341 --> 00:12:37.324
hot men UNK geheysn ⟨zikh⟩ tsudekn mit a koldre,

00:12:37.324 --> 00:12:39.358
un m'hot im do gegebn a koyl.

00:12:39.358 --> 00:12:43.813
⟨un⟩ do, az me git a koyl, geyt aroys a dine sh- shnirele blut,

00:12:43.813 --> 00:12:45.911
un me ken nit zogn afile "oy."

00:12:45.951 --> 00:12:46.766
glay-

00:12:46.766 --> 00:12:48.418
glaykh iz do der toyt.

00:12:49.933 --> 00:12:52.317
un m'hot undz, ⟨s-⟩ s'iz gekumen farnakht

