un m'hot ⟨undz⟩ ⟨aroyf⟩getribn oyf a sport-plats.

00:12:59.232 --> 00:13:01.719
azoy vi kh'hob aykh gezogt frier, vi in,

00:13:01.743 --> 00:13:04.774
vi AUSCHWITZ iz kegn di Karpatn, zeyer kalt.

00:13:04.774 --> 00:13:06.583
ikh hob gehalt a koldre,

00:13:06.994 --> 00:13:09.184
un ikh hob gehat tshekhishe shikh,

00:13:09.184 --> 00:13:12.252
mit dray por skarpetn ⟨zaynen⟩ ongeton.

00:13:13.069 --> 00:13:16.018
un ikh hob zikh geleygt shlofn in di shney. nit ikh,

00:13:16.018 --> 00:13:17.737
nor, nor, nor ale azoy.

00:13:18.334 --> 00:13:22.884
ober d- a sakh mentshn hobn nit oyfgeshtanen. derfrorn gevorn.

00:13:22.975 --> 00:13:24.625
eyner di oyern,

00:13:24.625 --> 00:13:26.106
eyner di hent.

