00:13:40.842 --> 00:13:46.256
vos me firt di k- beheymes, di ki, un m'hot undz avekgefirt nokh MAUTHAUSEN.

00:13:46.330 --> 00:13:48.470
MAUTHAUSEN, s'iz in Estraykh.

