un azoy, nokh a tsvey teg

00:13:58.738 --> 00:14:00.712
zayendik dortn do,

00:14:00.712 --> 00:14:02.914
ho- hobn zey gezen,

00:14:02.914 --> 00:14:04.382
ikh ken nit WALKen,

00:14:04.382 --> 00:14:05.741
ikh ken nit geyn,

