hob gevorn nit bay di gedanken, gevezn.

00:14:28.703 --> 00:14:32.072
dernokh, hob ikh zikh oyfgeshtanen. ikh hob gezen, ikh lig

00:14:32.938 --> 00:14:35.622
in, in, in a barak, in a betl.

