s'hot gedarft lign eyn mentsh,

00:14:42.837 --> 00:14:47.123
hot gelegn dray fun eyn zayt un tsvey fun anderer zayt.

00:14:47.123 --> 00:14:48.852
dos iz geven, dos iz geven de-

00:14:48.852 --> 00:14:50.629
kimat vi ende fun der milkhome,

00:14:50.629 --> 00:14:52.540
nayntsn finf un fertsik

00:14:52.540 --> 00:14:53.469
iz gevezn.

