un yede sekunde hot geshtorbn a mentsh.

00:14:56.631 --> 00:15:01.184
un m'hot im aroysgevorfn mi- mit di fis, vayl es zol zayn far mir merer plats.

00:15:01.184 --> 00:15:04.299
ober s'hot nit geholfn. bald arayngebrakht a andern.

00:15:05.305 --> 00:15:06.193
ikh,

00:15:06.520 --> 00:15:08.204
s'iz gegangen fun,

00:15:08.204 --> 00:15:10.732
fun mayn fus, vayl ikh hob nit gehat di finger,

00:15:11.262 --> 00:15:15.204
vayl ⟨s'iz⟩ geven opgefrorn hot ge- hot gegangen PUS, mit altsding.

00:15:16.712 --> 00:15:21.552
hot gezogt eyner a dokter, a Krokever dokter, SAM Rubenshteyn,

00:15:21.552 --> 00:15:22.410
hot er geheysn,

00:15:22.686 --> 00:15:27.087
"az du vest nit aropnemen di finef finger, vestu krign angrene,

00:15:27.087 --> 00:15:30.544
un m'vet dir darfn opshnaydn di fus biz danet o."

00:15:31.647 --> 00:15:34.104
hot er mir zey aropgeshnitn, di finger.

00:15:34.549 --> 00:15:37.816
keyn bandazhn iz ⟨dakht zikh⟩ nit gevezn, un m'hot nit gegebn.

00:15:37.047 --> 00:15:38.678
mit vos hot er geshnitn?

00:15:38.194 --> 00:15:40.958
ah? mit a, mit a PLAIN KNIFE.

00:15:40.958 --> 00:15:43.943
a, a, a geveynlekher meser, hot er opgeshnitn.

00:15:41.772 --> 00:15:42.913
a meser.

