un er hot mir gezogt, "oyb ikh vel dir nit opshnaydn di finger, vet men darfn opnemen a halbe fus."

00:15:56.591 --> 00:15:58.438
s'iz geven angrene, shvarts.

00:16:00.874 --> 00:16:05.349
un ikh hob k- tsugeleygt, kh'hob avekgegebn mayne MARGARINE vos ikh hob gekrign,

00:16:05.349 --> 00:16:06.844
a shtikl broyt vos kh'hob gekrign,

00:16:06.844 --> 00:16:09.418
hob ikh avekgegebn, ⟨er⟩ zol mir brengen a hemd

00:16:09.418 --> 00:16:11.179
fun di toyte mentshn

00:16:11.370 --> 00:16:15.447
un tsugeleygt tsum fus un gemakht b- ba- bandazhn fun dos o.

00:16:16.787 --> 00:16:21.219
un azoy hob ikh g- hobn mir gelebt, fir, fun,

00:16:21.698 --> 00:16:24.105
fun FEBRAL on, biz MAY

00:16:24.516 --> 00:16:27.851
⟨FIFTH⟩, NINETEEN FORTY FIVE, finf un fertsikstn yor,

00:16:28.262 --> 00:16:30.264
tsvey a zeyger bay tog,

00:16:31.975 --> 00:16:34.584
iz gekumen di amerikaner armey

00:16:36.177 --> 00:16:40.086
un zey hobn undz bafrayt. un ven di amerikaner armey

00:16:40.277 --> 00:16:43.919
kumt mit tsvantsik minut shpeter, tsu a halbe sho,

00:16:43.919 --> 00:16:46.802
hot men undz gevolt farbrenen lebedikerheyt.

00:16:46.892 --> 00:16:48.961
vayl ⟨es iz⟩ geshtanen BARRELS

00:16:49.238 --> 00:16:51.349
mit, mit GREASE,

00:16:51.349 --> 00:16:53.372
s- di smole, fun der loshn.

00:16:53.377 --> 00:16:55.593
m'hot undz gevolt farbrenen lebedikerheyt.

00:16:56.089 --> 00:17:00.701
un di amerikaner hobn dos gezen. m'hot oyfgeefnt di barakn, ale geheysn aroysgeyn.

00:17:00.701 --> 00:17:01.568
dos o.

00:17:01.860 --> 00:17:04.689
un tsugegangen an amerikaner, er kukt oyf mir,

00:17:05.319 --> 00:17:06.595
genumen redn,

00:17:07.480 --> 00:17:08.992
⟨zog⟩, "yidish, yidish."

00:17:09.049 --> 00:17:12.705
tsugegangen a yid, kh'hob im gezogt vos mit mir ⟨hot⟩ pasirt.

00:17:13.166 --> 00:17:16.091
un vi ikh hob genumen redn mit im, hob ikh gefaln

00:17:16.091 --> 00:17:18.375
un ikh hob ongevorn di gedanken.

