un in a por sho arum

00:17:22.718 --> 00:17:24.754
hob ikh gezen, ikh lig in a HOSPITAL.

00:17:25.435 --> 00:17:29.783
un di amerikaner hobn mir geshotn azelkhe pulver, mit nokh azelkhe zakhn.

00:17:32.083 --> 00:17:38.222
un dernokh hobn mentshn gekumen tsu forn, di italyener, polyakn,

00:17:38.222 --> 00:17:39.418
rusn,

00:17:39.576 --> 00:17:41.589
di ⟨BRIKHA⟩ fun ISRAEL,

00:17:41.589 --> 00:17:43.816
un m'hot tsugenumen ale

00:17:43.816 --> 00:17:46.354
yidn avu m'hot gevolt forn.

00:17:46.798 --> 00:17:50.808
i- i- ikh hob gevolt forn nokh Byalistok.

00:17:46.933 --> 00:17:48.057
zogt mir

00:17:50.832 --> 00:17:54.707
efsher vet efsher blaybn, geblibn lebn, mayn FAMILY.

