hob ikh geforn, zikh farshribn in a poylishn

00:17:59.303 --> 00:18:01.114
 organizatsye,

00:18:01.114 --> 00:18:02.351
un zey hobn mir,

00:18:02.357 --> 00:18:05.948
un zey hob- un ikh ⟨hob⟩ geforn mit zey, a transport mit di polyakn.

00:18:06.458 --> 00:18:10.856
hobn mir gekumen in der tshekhisher shtot ⟨Morave OSTRAWA⟩.

00:18:12.887 --> 00:18:17.623
