00:18:17.764 --> 00:18:19.462
oyb ir vilt geyn,

00:18:20.110 --> 00:18:25.200
kukn di shtot, dortn, ⟨tsu geyn⟩ krign esn efsher, mit altsding." hobn mir ale avek esn.

00:18:25.442 --> 00:18:27.073
mir kumen tsu geyn.

00:18:27.366 --> 00:18:29.438
der tsug iz avekgeforn.

00:18:29.438 --> 00:18:31.747
s'iz nishto tsu vemen tsum redn,

00:18:32.158 --> 00:18:34.544
mit di zakhn, mit altsding. dos,

00:18:34.544 --> 00:18:37.505
dos, dos hot men azoy geton, di rusn, az- azoy geton

00:18:37.505 --> 00:18:40.319
kedey hobn far zikh di zakhn, mit altsding.

00:18:40.275 --> 00:18:41.652
zogt mir eyn zakh.

00:18:41.743 --> 00:18:44.217
 lomir zikh kern a bisl tsurik.

00:18:44.494 --> 00:18:48.268
beys ir zayt gekumen in geto, in AUSCHWITZ,

00:18:48.595 --> 00:18:50.512
