geyt a TRAIN

00:20:13.414 --> 00:20:15.040
tsu Byalistok.

00:20:15.484 --> 00:20:18.026
hob ikh azoy geforn. ⟨m'hot⟩ UNK.

00:20:18.690 --> 00:20:20.726
s'iz gekumen n- n-

00:20:20.945 --> 00:20:23.429
n- nokh BRZEŚĆ NAD BUGIEM

