iz do a kleyn sht-, STATION,

00:20:25.977 --> 00:20:28.207
a tsvantsik mayl fun BRZEŚĆ NAD BUGIEM

00:20:28.207 --> 00:20:29.652
ts- tsu Byalistok,

00:20:29.760 --> 00:20:31.391
heyst zi CZEREMCHA.

00:20:33.625 --> 00:20:35.714
ikh gey arayn in vokzal,

00:20:35.714 --> 00:20:36.876
in STATION,

00:20:37.607 --> 00:20:39.744
geyt tsu tsu mir a polyak,

00:20:40.105 --> 00:20:42.326
zogt er, "⟨PANIE, ŻYDEM⟩?"

00:20:42.349 --> 00:20:43.828
"d- du binst a yid?"

