un i- ikh hob nit gevust vos do kumt for.

00:20:49.217 --> 00:20:51.894
zogt er, "ikh, ikh ⟨RADZĘ⟩,

00:21:02.329 --> 00:21:04.078
i- ikh ⟨RADZĘ⟩,

00:21:04.202 --> 00:21:06.946
ker zikh um mitn ponem tsum vant,

00:21:07.206 --> 00:21:09.765
