ikh hob nit di finf finger. ikh bin zeyer krank.

00:22:10.610 --> 00:22:14.396
vos vilt ir fun mir?" zogn zey, "kum shoyn arop. red nit keyn sakh."

00:22:14.723 --> 00:22:17.884
epes a- azoy vi me zogt bay undz yidn,

00:22:17.884 --> 00:22:20.825
di mame, ⟨olevasholem⟩, hot zikh gegebn a shtel avek

00:22:21.355 --> 00:22:24.808
un s'iz aroys dray rusishe soldatn

00:22:25.962 --> 00:22:27.424
fun, fun vald.

00:22:27.953 --> 00:22:29.904
un ikh hob zey gezen,

00:22:30.062 --> 00:22:33.313
hob ikh aropgeshprungen un ikh hob gelofn tsu zey,

00:22:33.522 --> 00:22:35.577
un ikh hob gezogt az di polyakn

00:22:35.577 --> 00:22:37.093
viln mir hargenen,

00:22:37.217 --> 00:22:40.369
ikh kum yetst fun AUSCHWITZ. ikh vayz zey dem NUMBER.

00:22:40.369 --> 00:22:42.071
ikh vayz zey di fis.

00:22:42.330 --> 00:22:44.183
hobn zey tsugegangen

00:22:44.183 --> 00:22:46.222
tsu dem, tsu dem ⟨PAROWÓZ⟩,

00:22:46.279 --> 00:22:48.534
aropgetribn di polyakn,

00:22:48.760 --> 00:22:52.933
un mir a- mir geheysn aroyfgeyn, un m'hot mir avekgefirt

00:22:52.933 --> 00:22:54.977
nokh BIELSK PODLASKI.

00:22:56.117 --> 00:22:59.317
ikh kum in BIELSK PODLASKI, ze ikh mentshn,

00:22:59.526 --> 00:23:02.104
freg ikh zey, "⟨CZY TUTY MIESZKAJĄ ZYDÓW⟩?"

00:23:02.104 --> 00:23:03.603
"tsu do voynt yidn?"

00:23:03.964 --> 00:23:07.113
zogt ⟨er⟩ mir, "dortn oyfn mark voynt a yidl."

00:23:09.111 --> 00:23:09.932
nu,

00:23:10.360 --> 00:23:12.774
hob ikh tsugegangen dortn un zogt,

00:23:12.774 --> 00:23:14.558
zogt er, "reb yid, ir vilt esn?

00:23:14.558 --> 00:23:16.007
zikh arumvashn?"

00:23:16.840 --> 00:23:19.264
zogt er, "ir vilt blaybn biz morgn?

00:23:19.337 --> 00:23:21.997
anit, geyt finf a zeyger far nakht,

00:23:22.172 --> 00:23:26.368
geyt a mashin nokh Byalistok. ikh vel batsoln," zogt er,

00:23:26.745 --> 00:23:29.582
"un ikh vel aykh aroyfzetsn, un forst nokh Byalistok.

00:23:29.582 --> 00:23:32.294
un oyb nit," zogt er, "kent ir shlofn bay mir biz morgn."

00:23:32.294 --> 00:23:34.823
zog ikh, "neyn. ikh vil forn nokh Byalistok."

00:23:34.710 --> 00:23:36.611
vi iz er geblibn lebn?

00:23:36.465 --> 00:23:37.302
ah?

00:23:37.647 --> 00:23:39.701
vi iz er geblibn lebn dort?

00:23:39.756 --> 00:23:41.505
er iz geven a partizan,

00:23:41.933 --> 00:23:43.479
iz, iz er gevezn.

00:23:44.818 --> 00:23:47.009
un azoy vi kh'hob aykh dertseylt frier,

00:23:47.009 --> 00:23:49.993
kh'hob gekumen in Byalistok, in tsenter shtot,

00:23:50.320 --> 00:23:54.036
vu ikh hob gearbet bayn restoran, fertsn gute yor gehat,

00:23:54.036 --> 00:23:55.764
gelebt beser vi a dokter.

00:23:55.872 --> 00:24:00.506
un ikh hob aykh gezogt frier, vos s- s- durkhgegangen a polyatshke un zi hot gezogt,

00:24:00.782 --> 00:24:04.404
"veyn nit azoy fil. di yidn amerikaner helfn."

00:24:04.495 --> 00:24:08.330
un oyf ⟨Minske⟩ gas iz do a komitet fun yidns helfn.

00:24:08.443 --> 00:24:10.462
nu, hob ikh dortn arayn.

00:24:11.177 --> 00:24:15.508
m'hot mir gegebn a ROOM avu tsum shlofn. s'iz geven shmutsik, mit altsding.

00:24:16.392 --> 00:24:18.478
oyf morgn in der fri,

00:24:18.822 --> 00:24:20.216
fort aroyf

00:24:20.408 --> 00:24:24.924
a droshke... ir veyst ⟨do-⟩ vos dos iz? UNK, mit a ferd, mit aza vogn.

00:24:25.521 --> 00:24:29.109
"⟨KTO TUTA PRZYJECHAŁ Z RESTAURACJI MANDELBAUMA⟩?"

00:24:29.183 --> 00:24:32.535
"ver iz do gekumen tsu forn fun restoran fun MANDELBAUM?"

00:24:33.418 --> 00:24:37.074
er shrayt azoy, ikh, un ikh her. hob ikh aropgelofn,

00:24:37.350 --> 00:24:39.438
iz gevezn eyner a polyak.

00:24:39.438 --> 00:24:41.664
er hot gehat a sklad ⟨APTECZNY⟩.

00:24:42.683 --> 00:24:44.870
ACROSS dem, d- de- dem,

00:24:44.870 --> 00:24:46.879
k- dem koshtshol, dem CHURCH.

00:24:47.020 --> 00:24:50.564
er fleg kumen esn bay undz dray mol in tog.

00:24:50.564 --> 00:24:52.036
er g- g- er hot gehat lib

00:24:52.036 --> 00:24:53.274
⟨gut⟩ tsum trinken

00:24:53.280 --> 00:24:56.159
un er hot gevolt nor oyf mayn zayt.

00:24:57.617 --> 00:25:02.337
un er hot mir derzen un er hot geshrign, "⟨EDEK, TY ŻYJESZ⟩!",

00:25:02.337 --> 00:25:07.770
"du lebst! du lebst!" zogt er, "du ⟨vest⟩ lebn do in dem shmuts, ikh vil nit."

00:25:07.770 --> 00:25:11.229
zogt er "kum, ikh vel ⟨dir⟩ avekfirn bay man tatn un ⟨bay⟩ der mamen,

00:25:11.742 --> 00:25:13.474
un du vest dortn zayn

00:25:13.632 --> 00:25:15.280
a por vokhn."

00:25:15.589 --> 00:25:17.439
un er hot mir gezogt azoy:

00:25:17.749 --> 00:25:20.934
"do iz nit gut far yidn, in Poyln.

00:25:20.934 --> 00:25:23.413
do iz a komunistishe land

00:25:23.413 --> 00:25:25.286
un a antisemitishe land."

00:25:25.596 --> 00:25:27.547
zogt er, "oyb du kenst,

00:25:28.093 --> 00:25:30.061
fort tsurik nokh Daytshland.

00:25:30.523 --> 00:25:34.623
fun Daytshland iz a ofene velt. kenstu forn avu du vilst

00:25:34.623 --> 00:25:36.266
un dortn di yidn beser

00:25:36.266 --> 00:25:37.722
vi in ale erter."

00:25:39.332 --> 00:25:43.505
glaykhtsaytik, ven ikh hob gevezn bay, bay zayn tatn mit der mamen,

00:25:43.505 --> 00:25:44.962
hob ikh zikh dervust

00:25:45.205 --> 00:25:48.878
az s'iz do mayner, der, er iz geven PRESIDENT fun Makabi,

00:25:50.031 --> 00:25:53.158
az er iz in ⟨DOLNY ŚLĄSK⟩, dos iz di ge-

00:25:53.158 --> 00:25:57.872
dos iz g- di gevezene, vos di polyakn hobn farnumen fun di daytshn, un er iz dortn do.

00:25:58.198 --> 00:26:02.531
hob ikh avekgeshribn a briv tsu im. kh'hob im oysgeshribn mayn lage,

00:26:02.531 --> 00:26:04.959
vos ikh hob tsores mit mayn fus,

00:26:04.982 --> 00:26:07.153
se geyt PUS mit altsding.

00:26:07.193 --> 00:26:09.853
hob ikh krign in a telegrame fun im,

00:26:10.011 --> 00:26:14.224
"⟨NATYCHMIAST PRZYJECHAĆ DO MNIE⟩," zol glaykh kumen tsu im.

00:26:14.753 --> 00:26:16.299
gekumen tsu im,

00:26:16.626 --> 00:26:19.441
mir gegebn a sheynem ROOM. er iz gevezn

00:26:19.441 --> 00:26:20.554
der firer

00:26:20.554 --> 00:26:24.517
fun di, fun di arestantn, azoy vi ikh, fun a groysn HOSPITAL.

00:26:25.232 --> 00:26:26.019
⟨iz dos⟩.

00:26:26.565 --> 00:26:29.478
un er hot arayngerufn a daytshishn profesor,

00:26:30.177 --> 00:26:32.348
un zey hobn mir batrakht di fus,

00:26:33.248 --> 00:26:36.077
un zey hobn aroysgeshnitn fun danet o

00:26:36.285 --> 00:26:37.935
a shtik ⟨t-⟩ fleysh,

00:26:37.935 --> 00:26:40.160
un arayngeton dortn in fus.

00:26:40.285 --> 00:26:44.602
oyf daytsh heyst es ÜBERPFLANZUNG, un oyf english ⟨dos zayn⟩,

00:26:48.334 --> 00:26:49.790
p- PLASTIC SURGERY.

00:26:50.038 --> 00:26:50.943
dos o.

00:26:51.034 --> 00:26:55.957
opligndik azoy a sheyne por vokhn in HOSPITAL, s'iz zikh farheylt,

00:26:56.097 --> 00:26:57.542
mit altsding,

00:26:58.155 --> 00:27:01.912
ober der antisemitizm in Poyln gevorn zeyer groys.

00:27:02.779 --> 00:27:06.969
s'iz geven a pogrom in KIELCE, a pogrom iz gevezn, un m'hot geharget yidn,

00:27:06.969 --> 00:27:08.797
epes etlekhe un fuftsik yidn.

00:27:08.820 --> 00:27:11.227
un mir ale yidn genumen loyfn tsurik

00:27:11.301 --> 00:27:12.940
nokh Daytshland.

00:27:13.883 --> 00:27:16.492
ikh hob genumen, ikh hob gehat dortn shoyn fraynd,

00:27:16.903 --> 00:27:20.390
un me, un s'iz geven dortn der Khaluts, di ⟨BRIKHA⟩,

00:27:20.582 --> 00:27:24.018
vos hot ge- gevolt nor ariberfirn di yidn nokh ISRAEL,

00:27:24.666 --> 00:27:27.346
un mir hobn bay der nakht aribergegangen

00:27:27.346 --> 00:27:29.689
di poylishe-tshekhishe grenets.

00:27:30.927 --> 00:27:34.138
⟨ye,⟩ hobn mir aribergegangen, m'hot undz gefirt, gefirt,

00:27:34.138 --> 00:27:36.843
aroyfgefirt oyf aza plats, un m'hot gezogt,

00:27:37.137 --> 00:27:39.555
"ale dokumentn vos ir hot,

00:27:39.555 --> 00:27:41.012
muzstu tseraysn,

00:27:41.642 --> 00:27:42.702
vayle,...

00:27:42.702 --> 00:27:45.689
un oyb imetser vet aykh fregn, ir zolt ⟨zey⟩ nit entfern.

00:27:45.689 --> 00:27:47.340
zogt im, "lekhu ⟨nerano⟩.""

00:27:47.937 --> 00:27:48.876
dos o.

00:27:50.181 --> 00:27:51.491
un azoy

00:27:51.497 --> 00:27:54.633
hobn mir gegangen, gegangen, m'hot undz avekgefirt

00:27:54.633 --> 00:27:56.891
aro- oyf di, oyf a ⟨TRAIN⟩,

00:27:57.538 --> 00:28:01.194
un m'hot undz ongezogt az mir zoln gornit redn UNK, vayle

00:28:01.521 --> 00:28:03.506
do in Tshekhn iz Rusland.

00:28:03.917 --> 00:28:06.374
di rusn veln visn az mir forn,

00:28:07.292 --> 00:28:09.615
ken men undz, ke- ken men undz fararestirn.

00:28:12.540 --> 00:28:14.592
hobn mir gekumen nokh Estraykh.

00:28:15.156 --> 00:28:16.443
nokh a
